Title: Ocean Data Platform R SDK
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "PÃ¥l Erik", family = "Lystad", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "pal.lystad@hubocean.earth"))
Description: Lightweight R bindings for the Ocean Data Platform services.
    The SDK focuses on authenticated access to tabular datasets exposed by the
    HubOcean API and currently provides read-only helpers for inspecting
    metadata and streaming batches into familiar R data structures.
